Poland’s Ruling Party Drops Flat Tax Plan, Gazeta Wyborcza Says

-- B y   M o n i k a   R o z l a l
-- 
2011-09-07T05:32:15Z

-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2011-09-07/poland-s-ruling-party-drops-flat-tax-plan-gazeta-wyborcza-says.html
Poland’s ruling Civic Platform
abandoned its plan to implement a flat tax rate, Gazeta Wyborcza
reported, citing Rafal Grupinski, the deputy head of the party’s
parliamentary club.  To contact the reporter on this story:
Monika Rozlal in Warsaw at 
